need = ['NOC', 'ID']
dataN = data.loc[:, np.isin(data.columns, need)]
dataSM = dataN.loc[np.array(data['Sport']=='Gymnastics')+ np.array(data['Sex']=='M')]
dataSF = dataN.loc[np.array(data['Sport']=='Gymnastics')+ np.array(data['Sex']=='F')]

#============================男性===========================================
tmpM = dataSM.groupby(by=['NOC']).count().sort_values(by=['ID'], ascending=False)
N = np.array(tmpM.axes[0].values)
V = np.array(tmpM['ID'])
V = V/V.sum()
for i in np.arange(12,V.shape[0],1):
    V[11] += V[i]
N[11] = '其他'
V = V[:12]
N = N[:12]
for i in range(12):
    N[i] += '\n' + '%.2f%%'%(V[i] * 100.0)
plt.tick_params(labelsize=20)
plt.title('男性田径项目国家获奖前十占比\n\n')
plt.pie(V, labels=N, startangle=50, explode=np.ones(len(V))/10.0)

#plt.tight_layout()
plt.savefig(r'D:\Pythonplace\可视化大作业\图片\男性田径项目国家获奖前十占比.jpg',dpi=800)

plt.show()

#encoding=utf-8  
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
fig = plt.figure(figsize=[15,10])
#定义x、y散点坐标
xWeight=data.Weight
yHeight=data.Height
x=xWeight.values
#print(x.T)
y=yHeight.values
#用3次多项式拟合
f1 = np.polyfit(x, y, 3)
p1 = np.poly1d(f1)
#print(p1)
#也可使用yvals=np.polyval(f1, x)
#yvals = p1(TMP)  #拟合y值
#print(yvals)
x=xWeight.values.reshape(-1,1)
y=yHeight.values.reshape(-1,1)

need = ['NOC', 'Year']

dataN = data.loc[:, np.isin(data.columns, need)]
N = np.array(dataN.groupby(by=['NOC']).count().axes[0].values)
Y = np.array(dataN.groupby(by=['Year']).count().axes[0].values)
IN = dict()
IY = dict()
for n in range(len(N)):
    IN[N[n]] = n
for y in range(len(Y)):
    IY[str(Y[y])] = y
V = np.zeros([N.shape[0], Y.shape[0]])
for i in range(dataN.shape[0]):
    t = dataN.iloc[i]
    V[IN[t['NOC']], IY[str(t['Year'])]] += 1
S = V.mean(axis=1) > 32
TOT = V.sum(axis=0)

for i in range(TOT.shape[0]):
    for j in range(S.shape[0]):
        V[j, i] /= TOT[i]

        plt.plot(range(35), np.reshape(V[i], [-1]), label=N[i])
